defaultATOC's mission
default 
defaultis
default to champion the interests of passenger rail operators in serving customers and supporting a safe, reliable, attractive and prosperous railway
default. Set up after privatisation in 1993, we bring together all train companies to preserve and enhance the benefits f
defaultor passengers of Britain’s national rail network. We also run joint industry services, including National Rail Enquiries, the Rail Settlement Plan and the discount Railcard schemes
